text=\"A\"><mi>A</mi></math></span>&nbsp;is a transformation matrix that maps the Preimage triangle to the Image triangle. Which of the following could define&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\"><mi>A</mi></math></span>&nbsp;?&nbsp;</p> </div> </div> </div>\n",
